{"content": "I need to multiply 952 \u00d7 594 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 952 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 952\u2081\u2081 = 9\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 2\u00d711\u2070\n- = 9\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 2\u00d71\n- = 1089 + 55 + 2\n- = 1146\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 594 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 594\u2081\u2081 = 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 4\u00d711\u2070\n- = 5\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 4\u00d71\n- = 605 + 99 + 4\n- = 708\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 1146 \u00d7 708 = 811,368\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 811,368 back to base 11**\n- 811368 \u00f7 11 = 73760 R 8\n- 73760 \u00f7 11 = 6705 R 5\n- 6705 \u00f7 11 = 609 R 6\n- 609 \u00f7 11 = 55 R 4\n- 55 \u00f7 11 = 5 R 0\n- 5 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 5\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 504658\n\n504658", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 389}